Hi!

I donk know what im doing wrong...

Im trying to make a custom email module that show a text depends on one property of a deal:

First im setting a variable with  that deal property (is a select/option field)
`{% set estado_visita = deal.estado_visita %}`

How can i check if this property is blanc, not option select:

```&lt;p&gt;
asign '': {% if estado_visita == '' %} null {% else %} not null {% endif %} &lt;br/&gt;
asign null: {% if estado_visita == null %} null {% else %} not null {% endif %} &lt;br/&gt;
asign unknown: {% if estado_visita == unknown %} null {% else %} not null {% endif %} &lt;br/&gt;
asign not: {% if not estado_visita %} null {% else %} not null {% endif %} &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;```
But all of this test return 'not null' even if this field have no chosen option, what am i doing wrong?
